<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1587] Propagating fl=*,score to shards</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1587</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When doing an HTTP request to a Solr Server using the shards parameter (&quot;&lt;em&gt;shards&lt;/em&gt;&quot;) the behavior of the response varies.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following requests cause the entire document (all fields) to return in the response:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&amp;amp;fl=score&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&amp;amp;fl=score&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&amp;amp;shards=shardLocation/solr/cpaCore&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&amp;amp;shards=shardLocation/solr/cpaCore&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following request causes only the fields &quot;id&quot; and &quot;score&quot; to return in the response:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&amp;amp;fl=score&amp;amp;shards=shardLocation/solr/cpaCore&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8180/solr/cpaCore/select/?q=*:*&amp;amp;fl=score&amp;amp;shards=shardLocation/solr/cpaCore&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t know if this is by design but it does provide for some inconsistent behavior, as shard requests behave differently than regular requests.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;any http solr server&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
